<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>แบบทดสอบความพร้อมทางอาชีพ (Full System)</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sarabun:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Chart.js/4.4.1/chart.umd.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #0EA5E9;
            --primary-dark: #0284C7;
            --primary-light: #E0F2FE;
            --teal: #14B8A6;
            --teal-light: #CCFBF1;
            --purple: #8B5CF6;
            --purple-light: #F5F3FF;
            --surface: #FFFFFF;
            --surface-2: #F8FAFC;
            --border: #E2E8F0;
            --text-primary: #0F172A;
            --text-secondary: #475569;
            --radius: 12px;
            --shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Sarabun', sans-serif;
            background: var(--surface-2);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .app-shell {
            max-width: 680px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px 16px 100px;
        }

        /* Header & Progress */
        .header {
            position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 50;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding: 12px; margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .progress-container {
            height: 6px; background: #e2e8f0; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; margin-top: 8px;
        }
        .progress-bar {
            height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary), var(--teal));
            width: 0%; transition: width 0.3s ease;
        }

        /* Screens */
        .screen { display: none; animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease; }
        .screen.active { display: block; }
        @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }

        /* Cards */
        .card {
            background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 24px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow); margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        /* Question Elements */
        .q-tag {
            display: inline-block; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .q-tag-a { background: var(--primary-light); color: var(--primary-dark); }
        .q-tag-b { background: var(--teal-light); color: #0F766E; }
        .q-tag-c { background: var(--purple-light); color: #6D28D9; }

        .career-title { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 20px; min-height: 60px; }

        /* Buttons */
        .btn-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px; }
        .ans-btn {
            padding: 15px 10px; border: 1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius);
            background: #fff; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s;
            font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500;
        }
        .ans-btn:hover { border-color: var(--primary); background: var(--primary-light); }
        .ans-btn.active-2 { background: var(--primary); color: #fff; border-color: var(--primary); }
        .ans-btn.active-1 { background: #94a3b8; color: #fff; border-color: #94a3b8; }
        .ans-btn.active-0 { background: #ef4444; color: #fff; border-color: #ef4444; }

        /* Ranking UI */
        .rank-item {
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px;
            padding: 15px; border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: var(--radius); margin-bottom: 10px;
            cursor: pointer; transition: 0.2s;
        }
        .rank-item:hover { border-color: var(--teal); background: var(--teal-light); }
        .rank-item.selected { border-color: var(--teal); background: var(--teal-light); }
        .rank-badge {
            width: 30px; height: 30px; border-radius: 50%;
            background: #e2e8f0; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px;
        }
        .rank-item.selected .rank-badge { background: var(--teal); color: #fff; }

        .btn-nav {
            width: 100%; padding: 16px; border: none; border-radius: var(--radius);
            font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.2s;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .btn-primary { background: var(--primary); color: #fff; }
        .btn-teal { background: var(--teal); color: #fff; }
        .btn-purple { background: var(--purple); color: #fff; }

        /* Results */
        .chart-container { margin: 20px 0; }
        .analysis-box { background: #f1f5f9; padding: 15px; border-radius: 10px; margin-top: 10px; font-size: 14px; }
        .career-list { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-top: 15px; }
        .career-chip { background: var(--primary-light); color: var(--primary-dark); padding: 5px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 13px; }

        .nav-footer { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-top: 20px; }
        .btn-back { background: none; border: none; color: var(--text-secondary); cursor: pointer; text-decoration: underline; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="header">
    <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;">
        <span style="font-weight:700; color:var(--primary);">Vocational Readiness</span>
        <span id="step-label" style="font-size:12px; color:var(--text-secondary);">เตรียมพร้อม...</span>
    </div>
    <div class="progress-container"><div id="main-progress" class="progress-bar"></div></div>
</div>

<div class="app-shell">

    <div class="screen active" id="screen-intro">
        <div class="card" style="text-align:center;">
            <h1 style="margin-bottom:15px;">แบบทดสอบความพร้อมทางอาชีพ</h1>
            <p style="color:var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom:20px;">ค้นหาเส้นทางอาชีพที่ใช่จาก ความสนใจ (A) และสไตล์การทำงาน (B)</p>
            <button class="btn-nav btn-primary" onclick="startTestA()">เริ่มทำแบบทดสอบ →</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="screen" id="screen-A">
        <div class="q-tag q-tag-a">ส่วนที่ ก: ความสนใจทางอาชีพ</div>
        <div class="card">
            <p style="font-size:13px; color:var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom:10px;" id="q-count-A"></p>
            <h2 class="career-title" id="q-text-A"></h2>
            <p style="font-size:14px; margin-bottom:15px;">คุณรู้สึก "ชอบ/สนใจ" อาชีพนี้แค่ไหน?</p>
            <div class="btn-grid">
                <button class="ans-btn" onclick="handleSelectA(2)">ชอบมาก (2)</button>
                <button class="ans-btn" onclick="handleSelectA(1)">เฉยๆ (1)</button>
                <button class="ans-btn" onclick="handleSelectA(0)">ไม่ชอบ (0)</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-footer">
            <button class="btn-back" onclick="prevA()">ย้อนกลับ</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="screen" id="screen-B">
        <div class="q-tag q-tag-b">ส่วนที่ ข: สไตล์การทำงาน (D/P/T)</div>
        <div class="card">
            <p style="font-size:13px; color:var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom:10px;" id="q-count-B"></p>
            <p id="q-text-B" style="font-weight:700; margin-bottom:15px; font-size:18px;"></p>
            <p style="font-size:13px; color:var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom:12px;">คลิกเพื่อเรียงลำดับ 1 (มากที่สุด) ไปยัง 3 (น้อยที่สุด)</p>
            <div id="rank-options-B"></div>
            <button class="btn-nav btn-teal" onclick="handleNextB()" id="btn-next-B" style="display:none;">ถัดไป</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="screen" id="screen-summary1">
        <div class="card" style="text-align:center;">
            <h2 style="color:var(--primary);">ผลลัพธ์เบื้องต้นของคุณ</h2>
            <p style="font-size:14px; color:var(--text-secondary);">นี่คือความสนใจและสไตล์การทำงานที่คุณถนัด</p>
            <div class="chart-container"><canvas id="radarChartA"></canvas></div>
            <div class="chart-container"><canvas id="barChartB"></canvas></div>
            <div id="top-career-box" class="analysis-box"></div>
            <hr style="margin:20px 0; border:0; border-top:1px solid var(--border);">
            <h3>ตรวจสอบความมั่นใจ (Test C)</h3>
            <p style="font-size:13px; margin:10px 0;">เพื่อค้นหาว่าอาชีพที่คุณชอบ คุณมีความสามารถที่จะทำได้จริงหรือไม่</p>
            <button class="btn-nav btn-purple" onclick="startTestC()">ตรวจสอบความมั่นใจต่อ →</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="screen" id="screen-C">
        <div class="q-tag q-tag-c">ส่วนที่ ค: ความมั่นใจในทักษะ</div>
        <div class="card">
            <p style="font-size:13px; color:var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom:10px;" id="q-count-C"></p>
            <h2 class="career-title" id="q-text-C"></h2>
            <p style="font-size:14px; margin-bottom:15px;">คุณ "มั่นใจ" ว่าจะทำงานนี้ได้ดีเพียงใด?</p>
            <div class="btn-grid">
                <button class="ans-btn" onclick="handleSelectC(2)">มั่นใจมาก (2)</button>
                <button class="ans-btn" onclick="handleSelectC(1)">ปานกลาง (1)</button>
                <button class="ans-btn" onclick="handleSelectC(0)">ไม่มั่นใจ (0)</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-footer">
            <button class="btn-back" onclick="prevC()">ย้อนกลับ</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="screen" id="screen-final">
        <div class="card">
            <h2 style="text-align:center; margin-bottom:20px;">บทสรุปศักยภาพรายบุคคล</h2>
            <div class="chart-container"><canvas id="comparisonChart"></canvas></div>
            <div id="gap-analysis-box" class="analysis-box" style="border-left: 5px solid var(--purple);"></div>
            <div style="margin-top:20px;">
                <h4 style="margin-bottom:10px;">กลุ่มอาชีพที่แนะนำสำหรับคุณ:</h4>
                <div id="final-career-chips" class="career-list"></div>
            </div>
            <button class="btn-nav btn-primary" onclick="location.reload()" style="margin-top:30px;">ทำแบบทดสอบใหม่อีกครั้ง</button>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>

